N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4235.2 - Annual registration; advertising symbols prohibited

State Regulations

Registration of colors, together with application for
owner's license to the commission, must be made annually. Colors bearing
symbols or markings for advertising purposes shall not be
accepted. Notes
